verses.text:
“Take of them of the captivity, even of Heldai, of Tobijah, and of Jedaiah;
and come the same day, and go into the house of Josiah the son of Zephaniah, where they have come from
Babylon.

Those who are far off shall come and build in the LORD’s temple;
and you shall know that the LORD of Armies has sent me to you. This will happen, if you will diligently
obey the LORD your God’s voice.”’”
